version_description: Works with piano and guitar. No capo, standard tuning.
Suits original better (I think) adds more fitting chords and plays nicer.
All parts included, corrected and timed chords.
Added the original Major7 chord which gives it a nicer touch.
This version includes Sean Paul's lyrics in addition to Sia's. Capo 2 to make the song easier to play.
Chords for Sia's "Cloud" from the album We Are Born. Standard tuning, no capo.
These are chords for Deer in Headlights.
The other version's lyrics are incorrect, this one has the correct lyrics, is more accurate and is tabbed throughout the whole song instead of leaving pieces out.
